<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id46c6af4c-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a" identifier="/us/usc/t26/s6315"><num value="6315">§ 6315.</num><heading> Payments of estimated income tax</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Payment of the estimated income tax, or any installment thereof, shall be considered payment on account of the income taxes imposed by subtitle A for the taxable year.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id46c6af4d-3a70-11f1-a967-d35dac11796a">(<ref href="/us/act/1954-08-16/ch736">Aug. 16, 1954, ch. 736</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/68A/778">68A Stat. 778</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
